'''Thoi-chhú''' he ngim yit-chúng su̍k-yî Thoi-chhú-muk ke [[Yû-thoi-thung-vu̍t]]. Thai-tô-su thoi-chhú tû-he [[O-thai-li-â]] ke thi̍t-sán, than-he Su-thoi-chhú chet sên-fa̍t chhai [[Pâ-pu-â Néu-kí-nui-â]]. 
Thoi-chhú-su̍k yû sâm-chúng: 

①'''Fùng-thai-thoi-chhú''' (Macropus rufus) he hien-chhùn chui-thai ke yû-thoi-thung-vu̍t. Fùng-thai Thoi-chhú sên-fa̍t chhai O-chû chûng-phu ke pan [[Sâ-mo̍k]] thi-tai. Sṳ̀n-ngièn hiùng-sin thoi-chhú ke thí-chhòng hí-khó tha̍t-tó liuk-chhak, thí-chhûng hí-khó tha̍t-tó kiú-sṳ̍p lióng-pak-pong.  

②'''Tûng-phu Fôi-thai-thoi-chhú''' (Macropus giganteus) sûi-yèn mò-yû Fùng-thai-thoi-chhú tén-miàng, than-he tûng-phu Fôi-thai-thoi-chhú he chui-sòng khon-kien ke. Sên-fa̍t chhai pí-káu phì-mî ke thi-khî.  

③'''Sî-phu Fôi-thai-thoi-chhú''' (Macropus fuliginosus) he sâm-chúng Thoi-chhú chûng chui-séu ke yit-chúng; sṳ̀n-ngièn hiùng-sin ke thí-chhòng he ńg-sṳ̍p-si chhiên-khiet. Sên-fa̍t chhai-yî [[O-chû]] sî-nàm hói-ngan lâu Tha̍t-lin-hò phùn-thi. Nang-ngoi yû lâu Thoi-chhú siong-kôan kín-me̍t-thi ke si-sṳ̍p kien-séu ke Thoi-chhú-muk:

④'''Su-thoi-chhú''' he cháu-to chhai tûng-pet-phu O-chû me̍t-si̍p ke yí-lìm kiên [[Pâ-pu-â Néu-kí-nui-â|Sîn-kí-nui-â]] chṳ̂n-sṳ̍t ke thoi-chhú ke su-muk chhîn-chhit. Kí-chak Su-thoi-chhú phî ngùi-hoi khi̍p, chú-yeu chhut-yì fàn-kín pho-fái.  

